1
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:49,520
Master

2
00:00:51,520 --> 00:00:52,840
I picked these nearby

3
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:53,640
They're for you

4
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:56,320
Thanks

5
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:57,040
Nida

6
00:00:57,280 --> 00:00:57,920
For now,

7
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:58,520
don't wander off anymore.

8
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:00,520
Over at Hong Ye's place,

9
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:01,320
you've already been exposed

10
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,640
We can't let their people

11
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,640
know you exist

12
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:04,360
Got it?

13
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:05,840
I'm not scared

14
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:08,160
I could've gotten away back then

15
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:09,680
Be good

16
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,520
Pretty, right?

17
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,520
This isn't the Death Jungle

18
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,920
It's more dangerous than the Death Jungle

19
00:01:34,240 --> 00:01:35,120
And another thing

20
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,640
He's my husband

21
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:39,840
It's not right to cling to him like this

22
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,200
So what if he's your husband?

23
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,400
In our tribe,

24
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,080
a real warrior

25
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,080
can have several wives

26
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,680
Master is so strong,

27
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,520
of course he can

28
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,200
She's kidding

29
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:51,880
Honey

30
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:54,480
Nida

31
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:55,640
Xingyu

32
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:07,080
Coffee

33
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,720
What do we do next?

34
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:20,120
Dr. Zhang told us to wait ten days

35
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,440
That means

36
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:22,800
for the next ten days,

37
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,600
we don't need to do a thing

38
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:26,920
and we'll still affect Hong Ye's plan

39
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:27,960
On the other hand,

40
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,840
anything we do

41
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,680
could end up ruining

42
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,080
the doctor's plan

43
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:37,120
Then why didn't Old Zhang tell us the plan?

44
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,400
At least we could cooperate

45
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:43,400
Some secrets are better left unknown

46
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:45,080
Trying hard to keep a secret

47
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,160
and not knowing it at all

48
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,960
are two different things

49
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,840
Am I that stupid?

50
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,640
I can keep my mouth shut

51
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:02,520
Oh, really?

52
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,520
You had a little to drink last night

53
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,040
and you blabbed everything

54
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,040
What did I say?

55
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,000
You said,

56
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,880
"Sis Fei told me to head

57
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:25,720
to the nightclub in an hour."

58
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:28,040
"Looks like she'll force us to seize arms."

59
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:30,840
You're not going

60
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,800
I still haven't settled

61
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,960
those past scores with her,

62
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:34,400
and she has the nerve to look for you

63
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:37,760
Don't worry

64
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,280
She's just testing me

65
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,760
Calling me there now

66
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,720
means I've passed the test

67
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,400
I still don't want you going alone

68
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,840
What if she turns on you?

69
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:50,680
Xingyu

70
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:53,200
In our situation right now,

71
00:03:54,320 --> 00:03:55,920
we're caught in the middle to survive

72
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,160
If we offend Sis Fei

73
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,040
and upset the balance,

74
00:03:59,240 --> 00:03:59,800
Hong Ye

75
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,360
will seize the chance to kill us

76
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,280
A micro earpiece

77
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:11,680
Stay in contact

78
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,720
If the signal gets jammed,

79
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,280
I'll need time to bypass it

80
00:04:24,520 --> 00:04:25,240
Stand down

81
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,400
Should I call you A Di

82
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,360
or should I call you Zhao Wudi?

83
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,200
Either one's fine

84
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,480
It's all the same anyway

85
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:38,360
To escape the Death Jungle,

86
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:39,720
you're the very first

87
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,160
Just got lucky

88
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,640
You called me here, Sis Fei

89
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:45,600
It can't be just to flatter me, right?

90
00:04:51,880 --> 00:04:52,880
Drink this

91
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,800
And everything in the past

92
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,200
will be wiped clean

93
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:03,880
A concoction

94
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,000
The Witch's Gift

95
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:08,800
That's right

96
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:11,520
Seven poisons mixed together

97
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,560
it's called the Witch's Gift

98
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,240
But

99
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,120
everyone's

100
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,480
Witch's Gift has a different formula

101
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,000
For mine,

102
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,560
without an antidote in ten minutes,

103
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,440
you will die

104
00:05:24,280 --> 00:05:25,880
I've got the antidote right here

105
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,560
Agree to one condition

106
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,600
and I'll give it to you

107
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,760
But first,

108
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,600
you have to drink this

109
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,160
Do you dare?

110
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:43,520
I admire that ruthlessness of yours

111
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,920
You're flattering me, Sis Fei

112
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:46,360
I knew it

113
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,760
You couldn't bear to kill me

114
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:49,200
Kick Hong Ye out

115
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,120
From now on, all your business

116
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,360
will be with me alone

117
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,280
I'm afraid that won't work

118
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:57,320
I've already signed a contract with Hong Ye

119
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,160
How about the three of us work together?

120
00:05:59,160 --> 00:05:59,840
Absolutely not

121
00:06:00,480 --> 00:06:01,640
Dongba's only so big

122
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:03,840
It's either him

123
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,120
or me

124
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,800
We're all just doing business

125
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:11,560
The cake can be shared

126
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:13,840
But we can't

127
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,640
hold the knife together

128
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,760
Well?

129
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,160
The drug's already kicked in

130
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:31,880
Agree to my condition

131
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:33,240
and I'll give you the antidote

132
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,320
Otherwise,

133
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:37,160
you will beg to live,

134
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,600
and beg to die

135
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:41,640
Stop struggling

136
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,560
A signal jammer is already set up here

137
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:47,240
Now tell me your answer

138
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,160
Otherwise,

139
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:50,400
the Witch's Gift will take your life

140
00:06:56,760 --> 00:06:57,840
What's going on?

141
00:06:58,080 --> 00:06:59,440
Why are there two frequency bands?

142
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,480
Could it be...?

143
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:07,760
Hey, A Di.

144
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:08,840
Can you hear me?

145
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,200
If you can hear me,

146
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,080
say the word "can" in your next sentence.

147
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,840
Sis Fei.

148
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:18,120
Can I get a glass of water?

149
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:19,920
Drink the liquor.

150
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,800
It'll ease the effects of the poison.

151
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,800
You've got eight minutes left.

152
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:27,520
Listen up.

153
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:28,960
Where you are,

154
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,960
there's another

155
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:30,960
encrypted device currently operating.

156
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,760
I suspect there's a mole around Sis Fei.

157
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,840
Your every move right now

158
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,240
is probably being monitored.

159
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,760
Understood.

160
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:40,960
Understood what?

161
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,560
I understand my own heart.

162
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,360
What I promised Hong Ye,

163
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:50,840
I will absolutely fulfill.

164
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,680
This is your choice.

165
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:07,080
This kid's tough as nails.

166
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,400
Even like this, he won't yield.

167
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,320
Does he not know this crazy bitch

168
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:12,240
could kill him?

169
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,120
He's not stupid.

170
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:18,200
This Feifei...

171
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,200
would absolutely never kill him.

172
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,720
What do you mean?

173
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:24,000
Didn't you see how Feifei looked at him?

174
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,040
Both admiration,

175
00:08:25,280 --> 00:08:26,280
and apprehension.

176
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,720
It seems this kid Zhao Wudi

177
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,480
is far more

178
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,320
useful than I imagined.

179
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:36,640
Based on the camera angle,

180
00:08:38,040 --> 00:08:39,280
the surveillance camera

181
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,120
should be in the corner to your right.

182
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,920
Based on the signal,

183
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,120
the receiver

184
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:45,400
should be on Hong Ye's side.

185
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,240
The mole around Sis Fei

186
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:48,240
was planted by Hong Ye.

187
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,880
Hello?

188
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:55,640
Hello?

189
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:02,840
Sis Fei.

190
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,640
What kind of drug did you give me?

191
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,680
A tonic.

192
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:08,640
It's just that,

193
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,840
with seven tonics mixed together,

194
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,640
the effect is way too strong.

195
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,840
It can drive a lion crazy.

196
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,240
If you don't let it out,

197
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,800
your heart and blood

198
00:09:20,160 --> 00:09:21,160
will pump wildly.

199
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:22,520
Then

200
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:23,600
you'll hear

201
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,800
a bang.

202
00:09:26,600 --> 00:09:27,920
If you want to live,

203
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:30,240
you need yin and yang to join.

204
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,600
Right now,

205
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,040
the only one who can save you

206
00:09:33,520 --> 00:09:34,920
is me.

207
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,040
Bad news!

208
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,440
Master fled into the woods!

209
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:01,560
We have to go save him immediately!

210
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:03,120
The woods?

211
00:10:04,320 --> 00:10:05,400
Wasn't he just at the nightclub?

212
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,920
Master...

213
00:10:07,120 --> 00:10:08,360
must have been poisoned.

214
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:09,480
He's so strong,

215
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,680
let's go draw the pursuers away.

216
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,960
He'll definitely be able to escape.

217
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,000
Get Ma Liu.

218
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,040
You sure it's here?

219
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:24,720
I'm sure.

220
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:25,880
I saw it with my own eyes.

221
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,120
Follow me.

222
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,600
President Xingyu.

223
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,720
Something's off.

224
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,640
Where's that little savage?

225
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:39,120
She was just here.

226
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,560
There's something wrong with Nida.

227
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:46,720
We need to get out of here fast.

228
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,640
Careful!

229
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,160
It's a trap set by the natives.

230
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,760
This place is too dangerous.

231
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:57,560
President Xingyu,

232
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,720
we've gotta find a way out.

233
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:00,280
Let's go!

234
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,840
As expected of the man I chose.

235
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,120
Doesn't it hurt?

236
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,240
It hurts.

237
00:11:36,880 --> 00:11:37,720
But it's worth it.

238
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,760
You're the gutsiest

239
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,680
most disciplined man I've ever met.

240
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,520
Sis Fei,

241
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:46,760
can we sit down

242
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:47,800
and talk business now?

243
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,320
Actually,

244
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:53,120
we could leave everything behind,

245
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,720
do some arms business together,

246
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,120
and then

247
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:59,200
run far away.

248
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:01,440
Far from all this fighting and killing.

249
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,760
I'm afraid I have to decline.

250
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,440
My family's got rules.

251
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:10,680
I can't overstep my place.

252
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:12,960
For business matters,

253
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,680
you'll have to talk to my wife.

254
00:12:26,640 --> 00:12:27,960
Oh my God.

255
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:33,160
Are we walking in circles in broad daylight?

256
00:12:33,440 --> 00:12:34,640
This is the fifth time

257
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:35,720
we've ended up back here.

258
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,520
We can't get out of here!

259
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:38,960
On the way here, I

260
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:40,280
set up five communication nodes.

261
00:12:40,920 --> 00:12:42,280
If we can form a comms matrix,

262
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,840
with satellite positioning,

263
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,320
we could find a way out.

264
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,240
But right now, all our signals

265
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,040
are completely jammed.

266
00:12:47,040 --> 00:12:48,720
We can't connect to the satellite at all!

267
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:53,680
The highest point.

268
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,320
There's a chance.

269
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,920
President Xingyu!

270
00:13:05,560 --> 00:13:06,480
Are you done?

271
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,640
I'm afraid of heights!

272
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:10,480
If I fall, I'll be a dead fat man!

273
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:12,360
Got a signal!

274
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:13,720
A bit higher, Ma Liu!

275
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:14,960
Still higher?

276
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:16,840
No, no, no!

277
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,440
I'm about to piss my pants!

278
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:19,240
Don't you dare piss.

279
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:20,800
If you do, I'll neuter you when we get back.

280
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,360
Hurry up, a bit higher!

281
00:13:30,400 --> 00:13:31,520
I'm so scared!

282
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:32,520
This way!

283
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:33,760
Come down, Ma Liu.

284
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,440
Careful!

285
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:39,600
President Xingyu, catch me!

286
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,720
Why did you tell her not to come see me?

287
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,280
If she really cares about you,

288
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:57,720
the more I send that,

289
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:59,200
the faster she'll come.

290
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,000
Didn't you say business matters

291
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,080
have to be discussed with your wife?

292
00:14:03,280 --> 00:14:05,440
If she betrayed Hong Ye first,

293
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,000
you don't need to follow the rules either.

294
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,720
Take Sis Fei's advice.

295
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:11,080
I've come to realize something.

296
00:14:11,880 --> 00:14:12,920
The older you are, the fiercer you get.

297
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,560
Are you calling me old?

298
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:15,640
You're not old.

299
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:17,240
But you're definitely fierce.

300
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:21,320
President Shen, you're later than I expected.

301
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,040
Don't want your husband anymore?

302
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:25,120
Took a wrong turn on the way and got delayed.

303
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,920
But the chemistry between my husband and me

304
00:14:28,760 --> 00:14:30,120
is something you wouldn't get, Sis Fei.

305
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:30,840
Honey.

306
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:32,320
Don't get the wrong idea.

307
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:34,480
Sis Fei just wants to discuss a partnership.

308
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:35,960
A partnership?

309
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:38,880
The bare minimum for a partnership

310
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:41,400
is sincerity, right?

311
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,360
Since A Di

312
00:14:43,880 --> 00:14:45,320
wants to play games with me,

313
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:47,640
I invited you both here,

314
00:14:48,120 --> 00:14:49,720
isn't that full of sincerity?

315
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:52,640
You want to make a deal behind Hong Ye's back.

316
00:14:53,400 --> 00:14:54,680
What a pity.

317
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,320
Your plan

318
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:58,320
Hong Ye already knows all about it.

319
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,400
Sis Fei.

320
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,680
It's hard to guard against an inside mole.
